@startuml
title Quiz-Taking Flow — Complete Sequence

actor       User
participant "PublicQuizLandingPage\n(/q/:slug)"        as Landing
participant "PublicQuizTakeView\n(/q/:slug/take)"      as TakeView
participant "publicQuizApi.ts"                          as ApiClient
participant "QuizController\n(NestJS)"                 as Controller
participant "AttemptService"                           as Service
database    "Repository\n(Mongo / In-Memory)"          as Repo
participant "Pinia\n(quizAttemptStore)"                as Store
database    "localStorage"                             as LS

== Load landing page ==

User       -> Landing    : navigate /q/:slug
Landing    -> ApiClient  : getPublicQuizBySlug(slug)
ApiClient  -> Controller : GET /api/quizzes/slug/:slug
Controller --> ApiClient : quiz data
ApiClient  --> Landing   : quiz data
Landing    --> User      : render quiz info & name form

== Start attempt ==

User       -> Landing    : enter name → click "Start quiz"
Landing    -> ApiClient  : createQuizAttempt({ quizId, takerName })
ApiClient  -> Controller : POST /api/quizzes/:id/attempts
Controller -> Service    : createAttempt(quizId, takerName)
Service    -> Repo       : repo.create(quizId, takerName)
Repo       --> Service   : QuizAttempt { id, startedAt }
Service    --> Controller: QuizAttempt
Controller --> ApiClient : { id, startedAt }
ApiClient  --> Landing   : attempt data
Landing    -> Store      : setAttempt({ attemptId, quizId, quizSlug, startedAt, takerName })
Landing    -> TakeView   : router.push(/q/:slug/take)

== Load quiz questions ==

TakeView   -> ApiClient  : getPublicQuizBySlug(slug)
ApiClient  -> Controller : GET /api/quizzes/slug/:slug
Controller --> ApiClient : quiz + questions
ApiClient  --> TakeView  : quiz + questions
TakeView   -> LS         : read localStorage[quiz-app-public-answers-{attemptId}]
LS         --> TakeView  : saved answers (or empty)
TakeView   --> User      : render questions + timer

== Answer questions ==

loop for each question
  User     -> TakeView   : selectAnswer(optionIndex)
  TakeView -> LS         : saveAnswers() — write answers map
end

== Submit quiz ==

alt user clicks "Submit quiz"
  User     -> TakeView   : click Submit
else timer reaches zero
  TakeView -> TakeView   : watch(remainingSeconds === 0) → submitQuiz()
end

TakeView   -> TakeView   : isSubmitted = true\ncalculate timeTaken
TakeView   -> ApiClient  : submitQuizAttempt({ quizId, attemptId, answers, timeTaken })
ApiClient  -> Controller : POST /api/quizzes/:id/attempts/:attemptId/submit
Controller -> Service    : submitAttempt(quizId, attemptId, answers, timeTaken)
Service    -> Repo       : findById(attemptId)
Repo       --> Service   : attempt
Service    -> Repo       : findById(quizId)
Repo       --> Service   : quiz
Service    -> Service    : calculateScore(quiz, answers)
Service    -> Repo       : repo.submit(attemptId, answers, score, timeTaken)
Repo       --> Service   : updated QuizAttempt
Service    --> Controller: { score, submittedAt }
Controller --> ApiClient : { score, submittedAt }
ApiClient  --> TakeView  : result
TakeView   --> User      : show results screen\n(score / time taken / question count)

@enduml
